    <item>
      <title>德国保守党通过新法案加强反移民行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/german-conservatives-to-double-down-on-hard-line-migration-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国保守党领袖弗里德里希·梅尔茨本周早些时候在极右翼的支持下强行通过议会决议，尽管遭到越来越多的反对，但他仍在加大强硬的移民政策推动力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/german-conservatives-to-double-down-on-hard-line-migration-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果战争增加数百万人感染疾病的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/war-in-congo-s-east-puts-millions-at-risk-of-infectious-disease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲首席卫生咨询机构表示，卢旺达支持的叛军与刚果军队之间的战斗已使数百万人面临因疾病蔓延而死亡的高风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/war-in-congo-s-east-puts-millions-at-risk-of-infectious-disease</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 16:42:55 GMT</pubDate>
